**Transitive trust assessment:** TG-01 and TG-02 represent transitive trust gaps. The bank cannot confirm the integrity of the foundation model's training data, and cannot confirm whether personal data of its customers was processed lawfully at layer 4. These gaps have been escalated to the CRO and accepted as residual risk pending resolution.
 
